room_title: Escape room "Comic Shock" by Key and Code Escape Rooms in Reno
room_address: 1180 Scheels Drive Suite B-103 Sparks, NV 89434
room_description: You hear a new little comic shop just opened up downtown. Your little cousin is obsessed with superheroes, memorabilia, and comics, and has watched all the latest movies. You and a few friends call for store hours and head that way. When you arrive, the door is open, but the shop is dark and seems closed. That can’t be right – you just talked to someone. You walk inside and soon uncover this store is just a front for the Shocker, an evil mastermind with plans of the darkest nature. Work together to thwart his agenda by experiencing yourself what it’s like to superpowers. Can you save the day?
